#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Appearance</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Uiterlijk</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can modify the various appearance related stuff here."
msgstr "U kunt hier de verschillende zaken voor het uiterlijk wijzigen."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Drop Target"
msgstr "Laten-vallen-doel gebruiken"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uncheck this if you do not want the &kget; Drop Target."
msgstr "Dit deactiveren als u het valdoel van &kget; niet wilt."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable animations"
msgstr "Animaties inschakelen"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables few fancy animations."
msgstr "Enkele leuke animaties inschakelen"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Groups"
msgstr "Groepen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can group downloads."
msgstr "U kunt downloads groeperen."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Groups</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Groepen van &kget;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Groups</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Groepen van &kget;</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use default folders for groups as suggestion"
msgstr "Gebruik de standaard mappen voor groepen als suggestie"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tick this box if you want &kget; to use default folders for your downloads."
msgstr ""
"Dit vakje activeren als u wilt dat &kget; standaard mappen gebruikt voor "
"downloads."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network"
msgstr "Netwerk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can modify your network related settings here."
msgstr "U kunt hier uw netwerk gerelateerde instellingen wijzigen."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Network</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Netwerk van &kget;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Network</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Netwerk van &kget;</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit Maximum Downloads Per Group"
msgstr "Maximum aantal downloads per groep beperken"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box if you want Download limits to be implemented."
msgstr "Dit vakje activeren als u limieten aan downloads wilt instellen."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed Limit"
msgstr "Snelheidslimiet"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box if you want the Global speed limits to be used."
msgstr "Dit vakje activeren als u globale snelheidslimieten wilt gebruiken."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global download limit"
msgstr "Globale downloadlimiet"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum global download limit."
msgstr "Globale downloadlimiet instellen"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global upload limit"
msgstr "Globale uploadlimiet"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum upload limit."
msgstr "Maximum uploadlimiet instellen."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconnect on Broken Connection"
msgstr "Bij verbroken verbinding opnieuw verbinden"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want &kget; to reconnect after an error or a broken "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Dit vakje activeren als u wilt dat &kget; opnieuw verbinding maakt na een "
"fout of een verbroken verbinding."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of retries"
msgstr "Aantal pogingen"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum number of time &kget; will try to reconnect."
msgstr ""
"Het maximum aantal pogingen dat &kget; probeert om opnieuw te verbinden "
"instellen."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retry after"
msgstr "Opnieuw proberen na"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the retrying interval here (in seconds)"
msgstr "Tijd tussen opnieuw proberen (in seconden)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Interface"
msgstr "Webinterface"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable the web interface, check <guilabel>Enable Web Interface</"
"guilabel>; default port is 8080, and you configure any port higher than "
"1024. Then set <guilabel>User</guilabel> and <guilabel>Password</guilabel>. "
"You can access your web interface at http://127.0.0.1:&lt;port&gt;. You will "
"need to enter the username and password to get access."
msgstr ""
"Om het webinterface in te schakelen, activeer <guilabel>Webinterface "
"inschakelen</guilabel>; standaard poort is 8080 en u stelt elke poort in "
"hoger dan 1024. Stel daarna <guilabel>Gebruiker</guilabel> en "
"<guilabel>Wachtwoord</guilabel> in. U kunt uw webinterface gebruiken op "
"http://127.0.0.1:&lt;port&gt;. U moet ook de gebruikersnaam en wachtwoord "
"invoeren om toegang te krijgen."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Web Interface</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget;-webinterface</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Web Interface</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget;-webinterface</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verification"
msgstr "Verificatie"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verify your downloads."
msgstr "Uw downloads verifiëren."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Verification</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget;-verificatie</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Verification</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget;-verificatie</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the two methods <guilabel>Automatic checksums verification</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> you can verify your downloads. You just "
"have to tick the <guilabel>Automatic verification</guilabel> check box."
msgstr ""
"Er zijn twee methoden <guilabel>Automatische verificatie met controlesommen</"
"guilabel> en <guilabel>Ondertekening</guilabel> waarmee u uw downloads kan "
"verifiëren. U hoeft alleen het keuzevakje <guilabel>Automatische "
"verificatie</guilabel> te activeren."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration"
msgstr "Integratie"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use as download manager for Konqueror"
msgstr "Als downloadbeheerder voor Konqueror gebruiken"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set &kget; as your download manager for &konqueror;."
msgstr "U kunt &kget; als downloadbeheerder voor &konqueror; instellen."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monitor clipboard for files to download"
msgstr "Klembord volgen voor bestanden om te downloaden"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can turn on this feature that asks if you want to download &URL;s copied "
"into the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"U kunt deze functie aanzetten die vraagt of u &URL;'s gekopieerd in het "
"klembord wilt downloaden."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Geavanceerd"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modify Advanced Options."
msgstr "Geavanceerde opties wijzigen."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Advanced Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; geavanceerde opties</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Advanced Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; geavanceerde opties</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable system tray icon"
msgstr "Systeemvakpictogram inschakelen"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "This check box enables the &kget; system tray icon."
msgstr "Dit keuzevakje schakelt het &kget; systeemvakpictogram in."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute action after all downloads have been finished"
msgstr "Voer de actie uit als alle downloads zijn voltooid"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to enable Quitting &kget; after all downloads have finished. "
"At startup you can choose to Restore Download state. Such as Stop All "
"downloads/ Start All downloads."
msgstr ""
"Dit vakje activeren om in te schakelen dat &kget; nadat alle downloads klaar "
"zijn, zichzelf beëindigd. Bij opstarten kunt u kiezen om de status van de "
"download te herladen. Zoals Stop alle downloads/ Start alle downloads."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "History backend"
msgstr "Geschiedenis van de backend"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose your history backend as Sqlite or Xml."
msgstr "U kunt uw backend voor de geschiedenis kiezen als Sqlite of Xml."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable &kde; global progress tracking"
msgstr "KDE's globale voortgangsindicator activeren"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set &kget; to show every single download or show overall progress."
msgstr ""
"U kunt &kget; instellen om elke enkele download te tonen of de algemene "
"voortgang."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Plug-ins"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Plugins Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; opties voor plug-ins</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Plugins Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; opties voor plug-ins</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can select the transfer plugins to be used. Use the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"pluginsettings.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to change the "
"default settings for a plugin."
msgstr ""
"Op deze pagina kunt u de te gebruiken plug-ins voor overdracht selecteren. "
"Gebruik de knop <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"pluginsettings.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"om de standaard instellingen voor een plug-in te wijzigen."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Hoofdvenster"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview of &kget;'s Main Window"
msgstr "Overzicht van het hoofdvenster van &kget;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Het menu Bestand"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Download...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bestand</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nieuwe download...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a new file to download"
msgstr "Een nieuwe bestand om te downloaden toevoegen"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Links...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bestand</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Koppelingen importeren...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Import Links</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Koppelingen importeren</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Import Links</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Koppelingen importeren</phrase>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action brings up another window, where you can see and manipulate which "
"file to download. Also you can make a selection based on <guilabel>Videos</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Images</guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Archives</guilabel>. There is also a text box to filter out "
"results."
msgstr ""
"Deze actie brengt een ander venster op, waar u kunt zien en manipuleren "
"welke bestanden te downloaden. U kunt ook een selectie maken gebaseerd op "
"<guilabel>Video's</guilabel>, <guilabel>Afbeeldingen</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Geluid</guilabel> en <guilabel>Archieven</guilabel>. Er is ook een "
"tekstvak om resultaten uit te filteren."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Transfers...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bestand</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Overdrachten importeren..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loads a <filename class=\"extension\">*.kgt</filename>, <filename class="
"\"extension\">*.metalink</filename>, <filename class=\"extension\">*.meta4</"
"filename> or <filename class=\"extension\">*.torrent</filename> file."
msgstr ""
"Laadt een <filename class=\"extension\">*.kgt</filename>, <filename class="
"\"extension\">*.metalink</filename>, <filename class=\"extension\">*.meta4</"
"filename> of <filename class=\"extension\">*.torrent</filename> bestand."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export Transfers List...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Bestand</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Overdrachtenlijst "
"exporteren...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Export the highlighted links to a <filename class=\"extension\">.kgt</"
"filename> file, to be loaded later."
